<p><i><b>HardBall!</b></i> is the first in a series of popular <a href="/wiki/Baseball" title="Baseball">baseball</a> <a href="/wiki/Computer_and_video_game" title="Computer and video game" class="mw-redirect">computer and video games</a> published by <a href="/wiki/Accolade_(game_company)" title="Accolade (game company)">Accolade</a>. It was released for a variety of platforms between 1985 and 1991.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
